Hi Jeyachandran! Welcome to the interview. I'm Master, your hiring officer today. Thank you for taking the time to speak with me. Before we begin, I'd like to take a quick look at your resume. 

From what I can see, you have some interesting projects and experiences listed. I notice that you've worked as an AI Project Developer at Shine Logics, developing a web app for mock interviews. Can you tell me more about that project? What specific technologies did you use and what was your role in the development process?
